======================
=  README for ex2:   =
======================

usage: Task 1: python3.3 ex2_square.py <positive_integer>
       Tasks 2+3: python3.3 ex2_rpsls.py <set_length>  <player_choice>	

==================
=  Description:  =
==================

Task 1's program draws a rhombus within a square on the screen depends on the input it receives from the user.
Task 2's program plays the "Rock-Paper-Scissors-Lizard-Spock" game for a player vs the computer.
Task 3's program plays the "Best of" mode of the game using task 2's program.

=============================
=  List of submitted files: =
=============================

README		This file
ex2_square.py   Draws a rhombus within a square on the screen
ex2_rpsls.py	Plays the "Rock-Paper-Scissors-Lizard-Spock" "Best of" mode, which is an extension of the game.


